module RanksHelper

  def rank_instruction_1
    "Optionally, company administrators can use JOB RANKS for deeper analysis.  With each job assigned to a rank, they'll be
     able to group categories of employees for the purpose of headcount studies, payroll analysis, absence issues, and so forth."
  end
  
  def rank_instruction_2
    "We set up a few typical categories here.  Company administrators can then modify the list to suit their own business."
  end
  
  def rank_instruction_3
    "The list is displayed in priority order.  Drag and drop using the red arrows to move an item to a higher or lower priority."
  end
  
end
